rows.label: bf11390150_0010
rows.name: Yo[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf11390150_0020
rows.name: Metsu[ML:Dash]

rows.label: bf11390150_0022
rows.name: I thought we had parted ways.

rows.label: bf11390150_0030
rows.name:
Not really.
It's not like I meant it as a final farewell.

rows.label: bf11390150_0040
rows.name: I went to see the Divine Beast of Iira.

rows.label: bf11390150_0050
rows.name:
It's gonna be fun to watch when that
thing finally shows its true colors.

rows.label: bf11390150_0060
rows.name: Where did you learn that?

rows.label: bf11390150_0070
rows.name: Nowhere in particular.

rows.label: bf11390150_0072
rows.name:
My Core is packed with all the data on every
Blade and Divine Beast there is.

rows.label: bf11390150_0080
rows.name: You have all the data?

rows.label: bf11390150_0090
rows.name: Do you intend to call yourself the Master Blade?

rows.label: bf11390150_0100
rows.name: I like that.

rows.label: bf11390150_0102
rows.name: Sounds good.

rows.label: bf11390150_0110
rows.name: So?

rows.label: bf11390150_0112
rows.name: Isn't it exciting?

rows.label: bf11390150_0120
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf11390150_0130
rows.name: I hear you handed my partner over to the Iiran prince.

rows.label: bf11390150_0140
rows.name: And if I did?

rows.label: bf11390150_0150
rows.name: Are you going to erase me from existence?

rows.label: bf11390150_0160
rows.name: Nah. I've got something much more fun in mind.

rows.label: bf11390150_0170
rows.name: I've decided to make Iira my next target.

rows.label: bf11390150_0180
rows.name: And you're telling me this, why?

rows.label: bf11390150_0190
rows.name: You can just sit back and enjoy the show from up here.
